text: Annadura C N is an Indian politician. He was elected as a Lok Sabha member of Tirubannamalai in 2019. He is a Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam politician. ==References== Category:Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Indian politicians Category:17th Lok Sabha members
